metadata.name: Treasure Crumbs Capsule Existential Crisis
metadata.description:
"To be, or not to be?"

[World of Awe Net Art](https://worldofawe.net)
[World of Awe @ Yael Kanarek](https://www.yaelkanarek.com/world-of-awe)

***World of Awe*** tells the story of a traveler who searches for a lost treasure in a parallel world called *Sunset/Sunrise*.

Yael Kanarek, 2023.
